            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Brilliant experience with DPS DLF City. My child joined the school 4 years ago. Me and my wife has always been following the ethics and rules of the school and it been an excellent experience to be a part of DPS family.  A special thanks to all the members of tthehe school to conduct the studies as well as co-curricular activities so well.  has taken another step higher during online classes since last year. Our  Gratitude to DPS DLF City for their unending and  sincere support.",
          "publisher": {
