          "datePublished": "2020-08-30",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "DPS DLF City is governed by DPS Maruti Kunj. Good campus. Lovely environment, good teaching standard. Qualified teachers all well behaved and trained. Greenery all sides of the school. Field is too big and well managed. Overall good school with good curriculum activities with affordable price. Maruti Group is playing good role to govern the school. Sometime unrealistic fee hike is a problem with this school. Overall 4 stars out of 5 from my side.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
